data.description: Beautiful, upgraded home in wonderful golf course community!! Open and bright floor plan offers master down, formal dining, open kitchen w/ breakfast area and large family room w/stone fireplace. Upstairs has wonderful gameroom w/four bedrooms. Gorgeous handscraped floors in entry, stairs,family, master gameroom, granite counters in kitchen, wrought iron staircase and from door. Lg. private backyard w/no rear neighbors. Full sprinkler system and water softener.Community amenities, pool,golf
